## 1. NFS 서버 준비
```
mkdir -p /export/k8s
chmod 777 /export/k8s
echo "/export/k8s *(rw,sync,no_root_squash)" >> /etc/exports
exportfs -rav
systemctl enable --now nfs-server
```

## 2. Kubernetes에 NFS CSI Driver 설치
```
kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes-csi/csi-driver-nfs/master/deploy/install-driver.yaml
```

## 3. StorageClass 작성
```
apiVersion: storage.k8s.io/v1
kind: StorageClass
metadata:
  name: nfs-csi
provisioner: nfs.csi.k8s.io
parameters:
  server: 10.0.0.5      # RHEL NFS 서버 IP
  share: /export/k8s    # export 경로
reclaimPolicy: Delete
volumeBindingMode: Immediate
mountOptions:
  - nfsvers=4.1
```

## 4. PVC 생성
```
apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolumeClaim
metadata:
  name: test-pvc
spec:
  accessModes:
    - ReadWriteMany
  storageClassName: nfs-csi
  resources:
    requests:
      storage: 5Gi
```
